GetUserCountry
==============

This is a simple Rails 3 plugin which gets the user's country name and country code.

Requirements:

1. Add to the Gemfile:
   gem 'carmen'
   gem 'hostip'






Example
=======

country_name = GetUserCountry.country_name #returns country name of user
country_code = GetUserCountry.country_code #returns country code of user


